snippet: A Republican primary runoff in Alabama that became an example of the internal battle between the establishment and the populist wings of the party ended with a victory Tuesday night for Bradley Byrne.
abstract: A Republican primary runoff in Alabama that became an example of the internal battle between the establishment and the populist wings of the party ended with a victory Tuesday night for Bradley Byrne.
